WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: tDswmiSXkVM

NOTE Language: en

00:00:18.189 --> 00:00:22.259
You are the One who offers happiness
and removes sorrows at the time of danger.

00:00:22.377 --> 00:00:26.362
You offer lots of tender
love and blessings

00:00:26.443 --> 00:00:30.428
You have red paste on Your body

00:00:30.512 --> 00:00:34.650
and wear a pearl necklace.

00:00:34.827 --> 00:00:42.716
Victory to You, most auspicious One!

00:00:43.065 --> 00:00:47.560
Even by Your glance
You fulfill the desires in our minds.

00:00:47.584 --> 00:00:50.562
Victory, O God!

00:01:01.693 --> 00:01:05.489
The Goddess Gauri
is present by Your side

00:01:05.854 --> 00:01:09.650
Bedecked with gems and jewellery,

00:01:10.203 --> 00:01:13.999
the diamond studded crown on
Your head adds to Your gracefulness,

00:01:14.108 --> 00:01:18.211
The anklets on Your feet make heavenly music.

00:01:18.303 --> 00:01:23.958
Victory to You, most auspicious One!

00:01:26.524 --> 00:01:30.678
Even by Your glance
You fulfill the desires in our minds.

00:01:30.719 --> 00:01:32.775
Victory, O God!

00:01:45.324 --> 00:01:49.256
I always have in mind Your big belly,
Your pitambar (yellow dhoti), Kundalini on Your stomach

00:01:49.298 --> 00:01:53.094
Your straight trunk,
Your innocent face with its three eyes.

00:01:53.425 --> 00:01:57.409
The servant of Shri Rama is waiting
for You in this house (body).

00:01:57.590 --> 00:02:03.740
Please protect us from calamities and sorrows.
O Highest amongst Gods, we bow to You!

00:02:03.781 --> 00:02:09.794
Victory to You, most auspicious One!

00:02:12.053 --> 00:02:16.224
Even by Your glance
You fulfill the desires in our minds.

00:02:16.265 --> 00:02:18.987
Victory, O God!
